Some artists have explored ways of continuing to produce and share their work via the Internet as an alternative to the traditional live show, such as live broadcasts of concerts or the creation of "festives" on the Internet for artists to interpret, distribute or publish their work.
Online, many Internet memes were spread over the coronavirus, as many resort to humor and distraction in the midst of uncertainty.
